reviewText: The first time I sa this film was in Mexico when I was 6 years old, it was recent at the time. Now that I'm an adult this movie came to mind and wondered what was the name of this film, Valentin T. has so many movies...but i knew that if i saw the film title i knew this was the one. This movie has tons of action, and the ending is pretty bittersweet. This movie rules!
